518
00:33:43,503 --> 00:33:45,152
No.

519
00:33:45,520 --> 00:33:47,104
We live on it.

520
00:33:48,911 --> 00:33:50,591
Just on our own terms.

521
00:33:52,495 --> 00:33:53,920
What terms?

522
00:33:55,472 --> 00:33:57,421
