00:34:48,815 --> 00:34:50,623
Ozaki's ordeal.

536
00:34:51,503 --> 00:34:52,992
<i>Life of Wind.</i>

537
00:34:56,110 --> 00:34:57,695
You doing anything?

538
00:34:59,310 --> 00:35:01,261
