00:35:29,775 --> 00:35:31,328
I don't.

545
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,512
We leave for the Alps first light.

546
00:35:36,687 --> 00:35:38,112
You coming?

547
00:35:41,936 --> 00:35:43,647
(HELICOPTER HOVERING)

548
00:35:50,702 --> 00:35:52,493
