00:37:43,150 --> 00:37:45,695
You heard the man. Pass the rock.

574
00:37:51,279 --> 00:37:52,832
(CHUCKLES)

575
00:37:54,063 --> 00:37:56,013
Oh, you funny assholes!

576
00:37:56,015 --> 00:37:57,933
Should have checked your bag, man.

