00:44:15,534 --> 00:44:16,556
(YELLING)

624
00:44:16,558 --> 00:44:18,060
Whoo-hoo!

625
00:44:18,062 --> 00:44:19,871
(CHEERING)

626
00:44:23,855 --> 00:44:24,909
Congratulations.

627
00:44:24,911 --> 00:44:26,464
Thanks, man.

628
00:44:27,566 --> 00:44:30,156
- Yeah! (GRUNTS)
- (LAUGHING)

