00:58:02,606 --> 00:58:04,479
giving back for that ordeal.

778
00:58:06,061 --> 00:58:07,422
How?

779
00:58:09,934 --> 00:58:14,828
He positioned his small
boat in the north Atlantic

780
00:58:14,830 --> 00:58:17,036
