832
01:02:21,966 --> 01:02:23,614
Where the fuck have you been?

833
01:02:24,589 --> 01:02:26,718
BODHI: <i>Ready to start
talkin' about giving back?</i>

834
01:02:33,806 --> 01:02:36,202
